node.text:
Which of these vibrant birds is your favorite? 1-10? 🦜🎨We can post your pictures in our account. Check the link in our bio for more info: @globefever (globefever.com) 

Names and Photos:
1) Silver throated Tanager - @jeffreypatrickkarnes
2) European Starling - @raheel.aazim
3) Mandarin duck - @eccentricwildlife
4) Golden-tailed Sapphire - @birddetective
5) Strawberry Finch - @praharsha_wildlife_stories
6) Periquito-rico - @macrotake
7) European Bee-eater - @dorugroza
8) Pink Robin - @ravi_arora
9) Keel billed Toucan - @floriankusterwildlife
10) Oriental Dwarf Kingfisher - @rahul_belsare

Breathtaking architecture spotted 🤯 Apply for a feature following the link in our bio and we will publish your photos in our account: @globefever 

Just 10 minutes away from Amsterdam, Zaandam is a pretty village in North Holland. 🎨

Can you describe this building with 2 emojis? 🌷

📽 @bodiek
📍 Zaamdam, Netherlands

node.text:
When you see your crush passing by 🦚✨Apply for a feature following the link in our bio and we will publish your photos in our account: @globefever 

A male peacock showing off his beautiful feathers to a female behind him.

Males have bright blue bodies, with green, blue, gold, and other hues in their tail feathers.

Females, on the other hand, have white, a greyish tone, and some darker shades on their bodies. They do have some green/blue on their necks, but nothing as striking as the males.

📽 @caenhillcc
📍 Caenhill Countryside Centre, Devizes, England
🎶 Sunny Day - Matteo Rossanese

node.text:
@Nature paradise vibes 🐠 We can post your photos in our account, follow the link in our bio: @globefever and we will select your pictures 

Situated in the Atlantic Ocean, The Bahamas is a tropical archipelago with almost one thousand islands. 🇧🇸

Did you know the story behind the sunken plane in the first shot? Read this: “This plane was owned by Pablo Escobar during the 1970’s smuggling era. It crashed when the pilot, high on his own cargo, missed the runway and ended up in the water. While the actual story is likely a lot less interesting, it still makes for a fun place to snorkel!"

From 1 to 10, which capture is your favorite? Who would you love to explore the @nature’s Bahamas underocean with? 🤿

📸 @jess.wandering @everchanginghorizon @matt.venturing 
📍 Bahamas

Is this the most beautiful mantis in @nature? We can post your photos in our account, follow the link in our bio: @globefever and we will select your pictures 

Flower mantises are those species of praying mantises that mimic flowers. Their coloration is an example of aggressive mimicry, a form of camouflage in which a predator's colours and patterns lure prey.

📽 @insecthaus_adi
